commit.message:
Add support for Process Blocking configuration (#10)

* RestrictEvents.cpp: Add process blocking configuration

* RestrictEvents.cpp: Add telemetry plugin block

* RestrictEvents.cpp: Fix declaration

* Revert non-functional telemetry patch

* RestrictEvents.cpp: Add MacPro7,1 model check

* RestrictEvents.cpp: Close statement

* Rename `pcie` arg to `pci`

Match revpatch argument

* RestrictEvents.cpp: Adjust

* Adjust to strlen

* Remove -1

* Set Post Increment and const to Blacklist

* Adjust variable handling

* Revert "Adjust variable handling”, use sizeof

This reverts commit bed2502f9c6fe7c7a859622121bbb2bc0c24a492.
